            <abstract>
                <p>A cosmological treatise of a European provenance, possibly translated from a Latin textbook on astronomy by a Jesuit missionary in 
                    Ethiopia in <date>the first half of the 17th century</date> (<bibl>
                        <ptr target="bm:HoffmannGeus2020Cosmology"></ptr>
                        <citedRange unit="page">62</citedRange>
                    </bibl>). The text was believed to be transmitted only in one 
                    manuscript (<ref type="mss" corresp="BNFabb109"></ref>) employed in all three existing editions, 
                    however, at least one further witness could be identified (<ref type="mss" corresp="BLorient816"></ref>). A preliminary 
                comparison of the witnesses show some deivergencies in readings.</p>
            </abstract>
